{3: 'Commandant Dormitory, Babylonia. 11:20 am. One hour away from the date with Bianca.'}
{2: "I should be there on time. Let's arrive 10 minutes early.", 3: '5', 4: "Can't keep a date waiting! I'm arriving half an hour early!", 5: '6'}
{3: '(50 minutes later.)'}
{3: '(30 minutes later.)'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory3.jpg'}
{3: 'The air feels fresh after a brief morning rain. A scatter of people walks by the road, and you notice the tall female figure by a lamp post from afar.'}
{2: 'Bianca!', 3: '10', 4: 'Why are you here so early?', 5: '10'}
{3: 'Bianca turns around. She is still equipped with her usual frame, but she looks different than usual somehow.'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'I happen to be free today, so I arrived a little early.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'The temperature is still a little cold. Based on what you usually wear, you might be a bit underdressed.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "It's getting windy at night. Here, please put on this scarf in case you catch a cold...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Th-thank you...', 3: '17', 4: "That's very sweet of you, Bianca...", 5: '17'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "It's what I should do.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "Let's go. We're heading that way.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'E-eh?', 3: '20', 4: 'Did you prepare something?', 5: '20'}
{3: 'Bianca walks toward a lawn by the side and takes out a blanket from her bag, laying it over the damp grass.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Bianca', 3: "You haven't had your lunch yet, right, Commandant?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Not yet.', 3: '25', 4: "Now that you've mentioned it, I'm getting a little hungry.", 5: '25'}
{3: 'Bianca sits on the blanket and opens the package she is carrying, revealing a series of lunchboxes filled with sizzling hot meals.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Bianca', 3: "I wasn't sure what you liked, so I made one of every cuisine I was good at.", 4: '1'}
{2: "That's impressive!", 3: '30', 4: 'Did you make all of this, Bianca?!', 5: '30'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'My previous... job involved taking care of other people.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'This is nothing out of the ordinary.', 4: '1'}
{2: "Then I'll get started!", 3: '34', 4: 'Thank you! They look super delicious!', 5: '34'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "There's tea for digestion in this cup. Please enjoy.", 4: '1'}
{2: "Bianca, you're smiling.", 3: '37', 4: "It's so rare to see you smiling, Bianca.", 5: '37'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "I guess that's because this reminds me of the past.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'It has been a long time since someone said something like this to me...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "For some reason, it's oddly comforting.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'It comforts you making food for other people?', 3: '43', 4: 'Then please keep making food for me in the future!', 5: '43'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "I-it's just... taking care of others has jogged some old memories.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "But if that's what you want, Commandant...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "I'm more than happy to comply.", 4: '1'}
